VCS -> Version Control System (Git)

WHEN YOU GET A JOB AND ON YOUR FIRST DAY
-Open a terminal (cmd)
-run java -version command to check if Java is downloaded on your machine
-run git --version to check if GIT is installed on your machine

-make sure that you have other set-ups - VPN
















